title: Converse Cons: Team Rider Absar Lebeh
description:
Hailing from Indonesia, Cons Team Rider Absar Lebeh talks skating and moonlighting as a skilled musician in his own band The Slave and in the famous Indonesian rock band The S.I.G.I.T.

Filmed & edited by: Janchai Montrelerdrasme
Original music by: Absar Lebeh
